Package de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.nodes.impl

This package holds all Nodes which are used by the DataNodes

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttackResultPrediction
    An AttackResultPrediction may be used to set the probability of a specific result of an attack
    BallPosition
    A BallPosition may be used to handle the position of the ball.
    PassSuccessPrediction
    A PassSuccessPrediction may be used to set the probability that the next pass will be successful
    PlayerHeatMap
    A PlayerHeatMap is a concrete HeatMapNode to handle the heat map of a specific player
    PlayerPosition
    A PlayerPosition may be used to handle the position of a player.
    PlayerStatistic
    A PlayerStatistic may be used to set all statistical parameters of a player
    PlayingTimeInformation
    A PlayingTimeInformation may be used to set all needed information about the current game time
    TeamHeatMap
    A TeamHeatMap is a concrete HeatMapNode to handle the heat map of a team
    TeamStatistic
    A TeamStatistic may be used to set all statistical parameters of a team
